1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,370
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,370 --> 00:00:02,370
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:02,370 --> 00:00:03,380
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:06,240
(Episode 84)

5
00:00:10,150 --> 00:00:12,880
Are you really Baek Jin Ju?

6
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:15,820
How...

7
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,490
How are you alive?

8
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:19,890
It felt too unfair...

9
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:23,360
for me to just die.

10
00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:27,370
Being betrayed by you,
a friend I trusted,

11
00:00:28,170 --> 00:00:29,330
was more than I could bear.

12
00:00:30,170 --> 00:00:31,170
I...

13
00:00:34,010 --> 00:00:35,110
I did nothing wrong.

14
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:37,940
He said
it would just be a minor accident.

15
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:42,250
I was simply following
Chairman Park's orders.

16
00:00:42,810 --> 00:00:43,820
Liar.

17
00:00:45,150 --> 00:00:48,320
You pushed my hand away
when I begged you for help.

18
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:51,220
After you hit me with a rock
and I rolled down the hill,

19
00:00:51,490 --> 00:00:54,130
the flames engulfed my dad and me,
but you...

20
00:00:55,230 --> 00:00:57,600
You ran away
using Park Tae Ho as an excuse.

21
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:02,370
In that moment,
you made the choice to kill me.

22
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:05,300
No!

23
00:01:07,340 --> 00:01:08,710
I was saving my own life.

24
00:01:10,110 --> 00:01:13,510
I just wanted to take back
what you had stolen from me.

25
00:01:14,180 --> 00:01:16,850
- What?
- I was studying design first,

26
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:18,950
but you jumped in later...

27
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:21,420
and stole the awards
that should've been mine.

28
00:01:22,450 --> 00:01:24,420
I liked Min Jun before you did,

29
00:01:25,390 --> 00:01:27,530
but you came out of nowhere
and stole him away.

30
00:01:28,860 --> 00:01:32,130
And on top of all that,
you tried to ruin my life.

31
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:37,170
You got my dad fired
and tried to ruin my life.

32
00:01:39,070 --> 00:01:42,440
Anyone in my shoes
would've made the same choice.

33
00:01:42,910 --> 00:01:43,910
Really?

34
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:46,880
Go on, keep making excuses
and see how long you last.

35
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:50,680
I will make you realize
that it was you,

36
00:01:51,220 --> 00:01:52,480
not me or Park Tae Ho,

37
00:01:53,220 --> 00:01:55,220
who ultimately destroyed
your own life.

38
00:01:58,290 --> 00:01:59,290
Don't take this any further.

39
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:06,530
If I tell Chairman Park,

40
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:08,730
you'll die all over again.

41
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:12,240
You know exactly
what he's capable of.

42
00:02:14,140 --> 00:02:15,640
I'll keep your secret,

43
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,080
so just end it right here.

44
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:22,780
You have a good life as Chloe.

45
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:26,020
A good life?

46
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:30,150
Hey, every time I see
you and Park Tae Ho,

47
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:32,160
I seethe with anger and injustice.

48
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:35,130
I had to fight the urge
to end my life...

49
00:02:35,390 --> 00:02:37,830
and I only survived
by relying heavily on medication.

50
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:42,670
Choi Yu Na, do you really think
I'm actually happy?

51
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:46,100
So?

52
00:02:47,610 --> 00:02:49,210
You're determined to torment me?

53
00:02:50,410 --> 00:02:52,310
You don't care
if I tell the chairman?

54
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,220
Yu Na.

55
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,850
Did you think I was
so scared of Park Tae Ho...

56
00:03:03,490 --> 00:03:05,760
that I'd beg you to keep quiet?

57
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:10,900
The one who is scared of him
is you, not me.

58
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:15,630
You're the one trembling in fear of
getting chewed out for messing up.

59
00:03:16,830 --> 00:03:18,740
Go run to Park Tae Ho
if you have the guts.

60
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:22,170
I came back to fight him...

61
00:03:22,670 --> 00:03:24,610
and that's why I waited seven years.

62
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,950
What do I do?

63
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,920
What am I supposed to do now?

64
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:45,000
What? Choi Yu Na found out?

65
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:48,970
Yes, it seems she was eavesdropping
on Hyun Jun and me.

66
00:03:49,170 --> 00:03:50,170
Oh, dear.

67
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,270
So, how did Choi Yu Na react?

68
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:57,140
She showed no remorse,
even with me right there.

69
00:03:58,340 --> 00:04:01,680
Instead, she was more worried
that Park Tae Ho would find out.

70
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:04,580
Honestly, between Park Tae Ho
and Choi Yu Na,

71
00:04:04,650 --> 00:04:06,080
I don't know who's worse.

72
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,920
I expected as much,
so I'm not surprised.

73
00:04:09,850 --> 00:04:13,590
She's too scared
to tell Park Tae Ho right now,

74
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:16,390
but she'll tell him eventually.

75
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:20,160
In that case, we should get
the ball rolling on our end.

76
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:23,770
The things you planned
to do as Baek Jin Ju, not as Chloe.

77
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,300
Right.

78
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:28,310
I have to reclaim every single asset
Choi Sam Sik stole...

79
00:04:28,770 --> 00:04:29,910
by betraying my father.

80
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:33,580
Of course. Damages,
return of illicit gains,

81
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:36,210
real estate, stocks,
absolutely everything...

82
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:37,980
We'll file
for a provisional seizure, right?

83
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:40,650
Yes, that's where we'll start.

84
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,650
Got it. Let's go all out.

85
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:50,530
I'll send...

86
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,770
these photos to Internal Affairs
as an anonymous tip.

87
00:04:54,470 --> 00:04:55,900
An internal investigation...

88
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,070
will be devastating
for a senior police official.

89
00:04:58,870 --> 00:04:59,870
Right.

90
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:02,940
We'll be able to cut off
one of Park Tae Ho's limbs.

91
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:06,010
I'll leak these photos to the press.

92
00:05:06,410 --> 00:05:07,980
Once the financial dealings
between Park Tae Ho...

93
00:05:08,050 --> 00:05:09,080
and Detective Yun are revealed,

94
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,950
it will prove
that Park Tae Ho has been lying.

95
00:05:19,790 --> 00:05:21,760
Honey, look at this.

96
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:26,430
What is it this time?
Why are you making such a fuss?

97
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,670
There's an article
about Chairman Park.

98
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:30,870
What? Is it another one
of those articles about...

99
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:33,240
whether Kim Dan Hui
or Park Tae Ho is the killer?

100
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,370
That's right.

101
00:05:34,370 --> 00:05:38,010
But it seems to me
that Chairman Park was the killer.

102
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:40,340
- You see,
- Yes?

103
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:42,750
that cop is on his payroll.

104
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,450
Really? Let me see.

105
00:05:45,550 --> 00:05:47,020
(Basement Dealings:
Police Brass Caught Taking Cash)

106
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:49,620
Oh my goodness. That rotten scum.

107
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:53,020
How can he do this
and still consider himself human?

108
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:54,890
Unbelievable.

109
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:59,230
Yu Na, come here.

110
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:03,430
You aren't still in league
with Park Tae Ho, are you?

111
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:06,070
What are you talking about
out of the blue?

112
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:09,240
Didn't you say you were
in the same boat...

113
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:10,410
after you got him out
of police custody?

114
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:14,010
Honey, really.
What do you take our daughter for?

115
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:16,380
She probably cut ties the second...

116
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:19,480
- his recording got leaked.
- Really?

117
00:06:21,890 --> 00:06:23,090
Chairman Park refuted everything.

118
00:06:23,090 --> 00:06:25,090
He said President Kim
was the one who...

119
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:27,460
Huh? Just read this.

120
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:30,930
This article says
Chairman Park paid someone off.

121
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:34,200
- What?
- Here, read it yourself.

122
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,470
Oh no.

123
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,210
For goodness' sake.

124
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,610
What? An internal investigation?

125
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,810
Are you saying
they found out about the money?

126
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:50,210
That woman, Kim Dan Hui,
took a picture and reported it.

127
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,950
How are you going
to take responsibility for this?

128
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:56,190
So, how much do they know?

129
00:06:56,490 --> 00:06:58,820
What reason did you give
for taking the money?

130
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:02,460
Tell them you took the money
for something else.

131
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:05,600
That it's unrelated to
what happened 30 years ago.

132
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:09,070
Hurry up and insist
that our evidence is undeniable!

133
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:12,800
It's no use.
No matter how much we deny it,

134
00:07:13,370 --> 00:07:15,970
they're still claiming
we framed Kim Dan Hui.

135
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,380
Thanks to you, I'm trash now too!

136
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:31,960
(Bit Life President, Oh Jung Ran)

137
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,030
(Shady Deal Between Park Tae Ho
and Police: Payment for Perjury?)

138
00:07:34,090 --> 00:07:37,730
Detective Yun. His love of money
finally caught up to him.

139
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,400
It's Deputy Chief Yun,
not Detective Yun.

140
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:41,600
You think he can keep his position
after this?

141
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:43,700
Then,

142
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,770
what happens now?

143
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:49,010
It's a 30-year-old case, so they
can't investigate properly anyway.

144
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:54,350
In the end, it all comes down to who
the public believes is the culprit.

145
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:57,850
This makes Park Tae Ho
Kim Myung Hui's murderer,

146
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:00,620
who tried to frame
another helpless victim.

147
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,850
He's become the scum of the earth.

148
00:08:05,090 --> 00:08:06,090
This round...

149
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,660
goes to Kim Dan Hui.

150
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:12,660
So, is that good for us
or bad for us?

151
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,430
We have to make it work for us.

152
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:19,770
What?

153
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:21,940
All right, here you go.

154
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,780
Everyone, grab a glass
and start with a toast.

155
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:30,980
- Na Yeon, this isn't alcohol.
- Who cares?

156
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,850
On a happy day like this,
you can call it whatever you want.

157
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:36,820
She's right.
We cleared Dan Hui's name,

158
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:39,190
and getting Park Tae Ho
and Detective Yun all at once...

159
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:40,220
is worth celebrating.

160
00:08:40,490 --> 00:08:43,360
- All right, cheers.
- Cheers.

161
00:08:44,830 --> 00:08:45,830
Enjoy.

162
00:08:48,430 --> 00:08:49,970
But where's Jin Ju?

163
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,800
She had something urgent
to deal with,

164
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:53,870
so she'll be a bit late.

165
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:56,670
- Did something happen to her?
- Yes.

166
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,910
Choi Yu Na has learned
Jin Ju's true identity.

167
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,650
Doesn't that put Jin Ju in danger?

168
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:04,650
If Choi Yu Na knows,

169
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:07,150
isn't it only a matter of time
before Chairman Park finds out?

170
00:09:07,890 --> 00:09:09,550
Where's Jin Ju right now?

171
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:12,060
Everyone, calm down.

172
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,960
I've assigned bodyguards to her
for her safety,

173
00:09:16,290 --> 00:09:20,030
and Jin Ju's charging ahead as if
she's been waiting for this day.

174
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:22,630
Fortunately, Park Tae Ho has lost
some of his power,

175
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:24,570
so we'll start with Choi Yu Na.

176
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:28,140
Even if Park Tae Ho has lost power,
he's still Park Tae Ho.

177
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:30,470
Now that he's been branded
a murderer,

178
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,310
if what happened seven years ago
gets out,

179
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:34,110
he'll feel completely cornered.

180
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:37,450
Then there's no telling
what he might do to Jin Ju.

181
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:40,750
Yes, that's why
I'm being extremely careful.

182
00:09:42,450 --> 00:09:44,990
I'll go see if Jin Ju is here.

183
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:09,110
Are you okay?

184
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:12,080
- What?
- Choi Yu Na knows who you are.

185
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:13,280
Oh, that.

186
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:16,390
- James must've told you.
- How did she find out?

187
00:10:16,450 --> 00:10:19,490
I was talking to Hyun Jun,
and I think she overheard us.

188
00:10:21,290 --> 00:10:22,930
That Choi Yu Na...

189
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:28,500
I'm worried my father
will come after you again.

190
00:10:29,100 --> 00:10:32,370
If Park Tae Ho finds out who I am,

191
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:36,610
I'll do what your mother did
and reveal my identity,

192
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:39,880
and demand a reinvestigation
into the case from seven years ago.

193
00:10:40,610 --> 00:10:43,280
With the police and the media
watching me,

194
00:10:43,610 --> 00:10:46,680
even Park Tae Ho won't be able
to act recklessly.

195
00:10:46,850 --> 00:10:49,650
Does Hyun Jun know
that your identity has been exposed?

196
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,620
He probably doesn't know yet.

197
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,030
I'll let him know.

198
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:59,260
Since he's with my father,
he can keep a close eye on him.

199
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,600
No matter how big
the misunderstanding is,

200
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,870
he wouldn't let you get hurt.

201
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:05,240
I'm not sure.

202
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,300
Would he really, though?

203
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:11,580
This is way past
a misunderstanding now.

204
00:11:11,780 --> 00:11:13,310
I feel like he hates me.

205
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,910
What?

206
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:19,380
I wasn't thinking
about his feelings...

207
00:11:19,650 --> 00:11:21,020
and inadvertently hurt him.

208
00:11:22,850 --> 00:11:24,390
That wasn't my intention,

209
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,790
but I couldn't explain
myself properly.

210
00:11:27,930 --> 00:11:29,130
What do you actually...

211
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,760
feel for him?

212
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:36,500
It's just...

213
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:38,640
I just feel guilty, that's all.

214
00:11:40,540 --> 00:11:42,840
Everyone must be waiting.
Let's go inside.

215
00:11:55,450 --> 00:11:58,760
You say all you feel is guilt,

216
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:01,530
but is that really...

217
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,530
all there is to it?

218
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,810
I've just met with Director Seo
and several other directors.

219
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,550
It happened 30 years ago,

220
00:12:22,610 --> 00:12:24,480
and the statute of limitations
has passed,

221
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:26,380
so you can't be legally punished.

222
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,350
But your crimes are so clear...

223
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:30,590
that no one is willing
to take your side, Father.

224
00:12:35,430 --> 00:12:37,930
But they're willing
to back Hyun Jun.

225
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:41,900
They think that if he makes
a public apology on your behalf...

226
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:44,740
and turns the public mood around
as the new young chairman,

227
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:46,070
it'll be a good thing.

228
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:53,010
A bunch of ungrateful,

229
00:12:54,450 --> 00:12:56,580
backstabbing fools.

230
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:58,880
If you don't want to lose
the company to Kim Dan Hui,

231
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,890
our Hyun Jun is your only option.

232
00:13:01,290 --> 00:13:02,290
You two...

233
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:06,190
If you betray me
and stab me in the back,

234
00:13:06,190 --> 00:13:07,960
I won't let you get away with it.

235
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:12,130
I'll kill you with my own two hands,

236
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,400
so you'd better get that straight.

237
00:13:14,330 --> 00:13:18,100
What? Are you saying
you'll hand him the chairmanship?

238
00:13:30,780 --> 00:13:31,780
It's me.

239
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:34,190
At the next board meeting,

240
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:36,150
I need to nominate my son,

241
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:40,190
Park Hyun Jun,

242
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:44,430
as the next chairman.
Get everything ready.

243
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:50,100
Hyun Jun. We did it, my son.

244
00:13:51,370 --> 00:13:54,040
- Thank you, Father.
- It's not over yet.

245
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:58,110
Stay sharp so you don't
get outsmarted by Kim Dan Hui.

246
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:00,780
Yes. Don't worry.

247
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:02,210
And Chloe...

248
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:05,950
Are you sure
you're completely done with her?

249
00:14:08,050 --> 00:14:09,050
Yes.

250
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:12,920
In my heart, she's already gone.

251
00:14:15,190 --> 00:14:17,560
Only becoming the chairman
of Adele Group,

252
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:20,000
that's all I'll think about.

253
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:36,380
Now my Hyun Jun is about to become
the owner of Adele Group.

254
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:39,920
But Kim Dan Hui is still a problem.

255
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:45,290
What if she reveals the secret
just to one-up Hyun Jun?

256
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:51,630
I should've bought her silence
by promising to testify.

257
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:59,970
(Ihwachae)

258
00:15:05,210 --> 00:15:08,180
The installation's finished.
Would you like a taste of the water?

259
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:14,920
This is nice.

260
00:15:15,990 --> 00:15:17,150
Thank you for your hard work.

261
00:15:17,620 --> 00:15:18,660
Thank you.

262
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:25,200
You really shouldn't have.

263
00:15:25,260 --> 00:15:27,430
Ever since I took over
the bio division,

264
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:30,130
I wanted to show my gratitude
with a nice gift.

265
00:15:30,430 --> 00:15:32,070
I'm sorry it took so long.

266
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:34,840
With it being this hot out,

267
00:15:35,170 --> 00:15:37,840
it's important to stay hydrated
with good quality water.

268
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:38,910
Sure.

269
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:42,310
Now that you've taken care
of the water I drink every day,

270
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:44,750
this will be a great help
in managing my health.

271
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,820
Thank you for the wonderful gift.

272
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:48,650
The pleasure was mine.

273
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:53,960
I'm the one
who should be thanking you.

274
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:57,560
Thanks to the tail
you put on Detective Yun,

275
00:15:58,230 --> 00:16:00,230
we managed to catch them
right in the middle of the deal.

276
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:04,470
And besides this,
you've helped me so much.

277
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:09,810
It seems I've also caused
some confusion, not just helped.

278
00:16:10,340 --> 00:16:12,180
I told you
that Baek Jin Ju and Chloe...

279
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:15,910
were different people,
but I was wrong.

280
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:21,090
It seems Chloe is Baek Jin Ju.

281
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:24,660
- Am I right?
- You recognized her.

282
00:16:27,060 --> 00:16:29,730
Yes, I met with Jin Ju,

283
00:16:30,090 --> 00:16:33,260
and I was able to find the evidence
that Dr. Baek left behind.

284
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,770
That evidence showed me
it wasn't Oh Jung Ran...

285
00:16:36,130 --> 00:16:38,600
but that Park Tae Ho was
the one behind it.

286
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,370
She saved my life.

287
00:16:42,370 --> 00:16:44,070
I'm so grateful to her.

288
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:47,640
So that she's not in danger,

289
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,250
I want to protect her.

290
00:16:49,450 --> 00:16:51,350
To protect someone,

291
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,580
you need great power.

292
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:58,660
I will add my strength
to your cause.

293
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:04,160
Oh no. What do we do?

294
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:06,660
- What do we do?
- This is bad.

295
00:17:09,230 --> 00:17:12,370
No way. You can't take this.

296
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,440
You rotten jerks.

297
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:14,840
If you want to put a sticker
on this,

298
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:16,470
you'll have to kill me first.

299
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:18,240
No, just kill me.

300
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:20,540
I can't let you take this!

301
00:17:22,210 --> 00:17:24,180
- Oh, dear.
- Let's go.

302
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:30,050
My gosh. What do we do? Oh no.

303
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:34,860
What in the world did you do wrong?

304
00:17:35,090 --> 00:17:38,060
What did you do
to make them seize everything...

305
00:17:38,100 --> 00:17:40,060
from our shares
to the things in our own home?

306
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:43,130
I don't know what's going on.

307
00:17:43,430 --> 00:17:45,640
They're using the company sale
from seven years ago...

308
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:47,670
to sue for damages
and freeze our assets.

309
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:50,870
But Chairman Park definitely...

310
00:17:51,210 --> 00:17:53,380
- took care of everything back then.
- What?

311
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:57,710
Are you telling me you actually
did something to deserve this?

312
00:17:58,650 --> 00:18:01,190
Was this Jin Ju's doing?

313
00:18:01,250 --> 00:18:02,320
What?

314
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:07,890
What on earth? Isn't that Clyde?

315
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:22,540
This is all your doing, isn't it?

316
00:18:22,910 --> 00:18:25,180
So, you're starting
by taking my family's fortune?

317
00:18:25,410 --> 00:18:29,050
Yu Na, let's be clear about this.

318
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:30,980
I'm not taking anything.

319
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:33,220
I'm taking back
what was stolen from me...

320
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:35,590
on behalf of my father.

321
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:37,860
Your father?

322
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:40,760
What is this all about?

323
00:18:40,890 --> 00:18:43,890
All this time,
you've been living in comfort...

324
00:18:44,430 --> 00:18:46,360
at the cost of my father's life.

325
00:18:47,730 --> 00:18:50,670
Now, hand it all back over.

326
00:18:51,170 --> 00:18:52,170
What?

327
00:18:52,870 --> 00:18:54,440
Are you...

328
00:18:54,540 --> 00:18:58,210
Are you saying you're...

329
00:18:58,280 --> 00:19:01,010
That's right! It's me.

330
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:02,980
Baek Jun Gi's daughter,

331
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,980
Baek Jin Ju.

332
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:06,820
Jin Ju?

333
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:09,590
Oh my.

334
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:11,890
What in the world is going on?

335
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:15,130
Wait. How can a dead girl...

336
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:16,160
Yu Na.

337
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:19,160
You said her name was Clyde.

338
00:19:19,530 --> 00:19:21,470
How did Clyde become Baek Jin Ju?

339
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:24,540
She's been deceiving us.

340
00:19:25,470 --> 00:19:26,700
She really is Baek Jin Ju.

341
00:19:28,570 --> 00:19:31,010
Then, are you telling me...

342
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:34,610
Jin Ju returned to us alive...

343
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:37,880
and completely tore
our lives apart? Why?

344
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,650
My goodness.

345
00:19:42,490 --> 00:19:46,290
Jin Ju. If you really are Jin Ju,

346
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:48,730
you can't do this to us.

347
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:51,660
We were so good to you
and your father.

348
00:19:52,130 --> 00:19:54,530
There's a limit
to repaying kindness with evil.

349
00:19:54,670 --> 00:19:57,870
Exactly. So why, Mr. Choi,
would you repay kindness...

350
00:19:58,570 --> 00:20:00,240
with betrayal?

351
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:03,110
You betrayed my father
and sold off his company.

352
00:20:03,410 --> 00:20:04,980
You forged his will
and framed him...

353
00:20:04,980 --> 00:20:07,410
for embezzlement
and breach of trust.

354
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:10,650
He did what? Honey.

355
00:20:12,450 --> 00:20:15,790
I never meant for that to happen.

356
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:19,990
Chairman Park tempted me
to hand over the company.

357
00:20:20,090 --> 00:20:24,160
The will and the press conference
were all his doing.

358
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:30,230
Are you saying Chairman Park planned
everything from start to finish?

359
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:31,600
Yes.

360
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:37,140
I was just doing
what Chairman Park told me.

361
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:39,440
Save the excuses.

362
00:20:40,780 --> 00:20:44,550
Just following orders
doesn't make you any less guilty.

363
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,750
You and Yu Na...

364
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:51,720
are the ones
who killed me and my father.

365
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:55,660
You're murderers.

366
00:20:56,290 --> 00:20:57,290
What...

367
00:20:57,630 --> 00:21:01,230
Murderers?

368
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:08,740
Oh my. Honey!
Goodness, what do we do?

369
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:10,070
Yu Na!

370
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:12,940
Baek Jin Ju!

371
00:21:14,010 --> 00:21:15,610
Because of you people...

372
00:21:16,780 --> 00:21:19,550
Because of you pathetic people,

373
00:21:22,090 --> 00:21:23,850
my dad died.

374
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:28,660
While you...

375
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:33,160
were in this house laughing,

376
00:21:34,230 --> 00:21:37,400
chatting, and living comfortably,

377
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:40,900
- I was in agony,
- Oh, dear.

378
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:44,510
howling like a monster
every single night.

379
00:21:46,210 --> 00:21:49,310
Now, just like me,

380
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:54,020
you'll have to live every night
in agony.

381
00:21:56,220 --> 00:22:00,560
What do we do? Oh my.

382
00:22:01,530 --> 00:22:05,160
Yu Na, this isn't true, is it?

383
00:22:05,430 --> 00:22:07,160
This is all nonsense, right?

384
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:11,070
My goodness, please say something.

385
00:22:11,070 --> 00:22:12,370
Your daughter...

386
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:16,840
conspired with Park Tae Ho
and harmed CEO Baek.

387
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:18,640
When someone takes a life,

388
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:22,580
you're supposed to teach them...

389
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:25,580
to feel remorse to make them repent.

390
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,020
Please!

391
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:32,890
My gosh, oh no.

392
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,130
Oh, dear.

393
00:22:37,330 --> 00:22:40,260
What's happening? What am I to do?

394
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,130
Oh, dear.

395
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,170
Oh no.

396
00:22:49,270 --> 00:22:50,770
My gosh.

397
00:23:16,530 --> 00:23:17,900
That must've been rough.

398
00:23:22,970 --> 00:23:24,940
I thought I'd feel
a sense of relief.

399
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:31,480
After getting my revenge
on the people who betrayed my dad,

400
00:23:32,980 --> 00:23:34,280
I thought this feeling
of being wronged...

401
00:23:35,290 --> 00:23:37,250
would ease a little.

402
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:40,760
Strangely,

403
00:23:41,660 --> 00:23:43,160
my heart aches even more.

404
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:50,800
I'm reminded of my dad.

405
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:55,110
My dad, who was wronged so deeply...

406
00:23:57,940 --> 00:23:59,310
It hurts so much.

407
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:12,560
We're almost there.

408
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:14,720
We're almost there.

409
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:19,300
Let's go.

410
00:24:27,570 --> 00:24:31,440
- What's all this?
- Can't you tell? They're gifts.

411
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:35,380
Did you put poison
in this expensive food?

412
00:24:39,420 --> 00:24:41,320
I came here to talk.

413
00:24:42,650 --> 00:24:44,450
With you, Kim Dan Hui. In private.

414
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:50,130
Yoon Jung,
could you give us a moment?

415
00:24:52,330 --> 00:24:53,860
Are you sure you'll be okay?

416
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,270
I'll be fine.

417
00:24:57,330 --> 00:25:00,470
If things get dangerous,
call for me right away.

418
00:25:00,970 --> 00:25:01,970
Got it?

419
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:08,610
Geun Tae, you should leave too.

420
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,880
What?

421
00:25:12,250 --> 00:25:13,720
Oh, all right.

422
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:22,960
Are you here about Hyun Jun?

423
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:24,730
You're always so sharp.

424
00:25:24,830 --> 00:25:27,360
If Park Tae Ho is unable to return,

425
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:30,270
you'll have to make Hyun Jun
the chairman.

426
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:35,040
You must be scared
I'd expose Hyun Jun's secret.

427
00:25:36,740 --> 00:25:39,380
Well, I'm not exactly scared.

428
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,750
More like, a little concerned.

429
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:46,350
So, how about we make a deal?

430
00:25:46,580 --> 00:25:47,580
A deal?

431
00:25:49,190 --> 00:25:51,620
If you let my Hyun Jun
become chairman,

432
00:25:51,660 --> 00:25:53,960
I'll help you take down Park Tae Ho.

433
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:57,230
Just tell me what you want.

434
00:25:57,490 --> 00:26:00,400
You'll give me anything I want?

435
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:02,770
Just name your price.

436
00:26:02,770 --> 00:26:06,700
Park Tae Ho's slush fund ledger,
containing all of his corruption.

437
00:26:07,470 --> 00:26:11,510
And testimony that Park Tae Ho
killed CEO Baek Jun Gi.

438
00:26:12,210 --> 00:26:15,750
Promise me those two things,
and I'll keep Hyun Jun's secret.

439
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:18,650
Why are your terms so difficult?

440
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,480
Think it over
by the next board meeting.

441
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,920
Kim Dan Hui.

442
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:57,320
Because of Kim Dan Hui...

443
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:00,420
If only that secret
from 30 years ago...

444
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:03,260
hadn't been found out.

445
00:27:14,570 --> 00:27:16,470
Park Tae Ho's slush fund ledger.

446
00:27:18,210 --> 00:27:20,980
If I hand that over,
she'll keep Hyun Jun's secret?

447
00:27:21,780 --> 00:27:23,680
Once that jerk is in prison,

448
00:27:24,850 --> 00:27:27,380
does that mean Hyun Jun is
in complete control of Adele?

449
00:27:43,900 --> 00:27:45,840
Are you taking turns to bother me?

450
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:49,870
First Baek Jin Ju, and now you?

451
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:52,610
Choi Yu Na found out
Jin Ju's true identity.

452
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,640
What?

453
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:58,010
She heard you
calling her Baek Jin Ju.

454
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:03,850
Now that Choi Yu Na knows,
Father will find out soon.

455
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,960
To hide what happened
seven years ago,

456
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:08,890
he might go after Jin Ju again.

457
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:14,460
So what do you want me to do?

458
00:28:14,830 --> 00:28:15,830
Protect her.

459
00:28:17,570 --> 00:28:19,900
You're by Father's side,
so you can watch him.

460
00:28:20,340 --> 00:28:22,970
Please protect Jin Ju
from any fallout.

461
00:28:28,810 --> 00:28:30,610
Handle it yourself.

462
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:33,380
I don't have the time
to protect someone...

463
00:28:34,850 --> 00:28:36,290
who betrayed me.

464
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,720
If something happens to Jin Ju,

465
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:40,190
you'll never be able
to forgive yourself.

466
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:42,030
And neither will I.

467
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:46,660
Call me if anything happens.

468
00:28:48,230 --> 00:28:49,230
I'm counting on you.

469
00:29:08,350 --> 00:29:09,520
So you're saying...

470
00:29:11,620 --> 00:29:12,620
that you really...

471
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:15,560
killed CEO Baek?

472
00:29:15,890 --> 00:29:17,030
I was tricked too.

473
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:19,930
I thought Chairman Park was
only planning a minor accident.

474
00:29:20,430 --> 00:29:22,430
I had no idea
the car would actually explode.

475
00:29:24,630 --> 00:29:27,270
So the police were right
to arrest him on bomb charges.

476
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:30,010
Then what about Jin Ju?

477
00:29:30,610 --> 00:29:31,840
When you knew she was alive,

478
00:29:32,140 --> 00:29:34,180
didn't you even think
to change your mind?

479
00:29:34,180 --> 00:29:35,510
How could I?

480
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:37,410
If Jin Ju is alive,
I'm completely erased.

481
00:29:37,710 --> 00:29:41,850
You crazy girl. You pathetic child.

482
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:43,290
What are we going to do now?

483
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:47,760
Jin Ju is breathing fire
and out to destroy us all!

484
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:49,960
I don't know.

485
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,230
I don't know what I can do.

486
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:55,670
Oh no. What do we do?

487
00:29:56,570 --> 00:29:57,670
That's it.

488
00:29:58,330 --> 00:29:59,440
Park Tae Ho.

489
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:02,140
We'll go to that darn Park Tae Ho...

490
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,640
and make him take responsibility.

491
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,840
No, not him.

492
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:07,380
If he finds out
I failed to kill Jin Ju,

493
00:30:07,810 --> 00:30:08,980
he'll destroy me.

494
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,710
Darn it all.

495
00:30:11,150 --> 00:30:14,220
There's no way I'm letting
that jerk walk away clean.

496
00:30:14,980 --> 00:30:16,020
I said stop it.

497
00:30:16,850 --> 00:30:18,050
It's no use anyway.

498
00:30:18,050 --> 00:30:20,660
He was ousted as chairman
and is now exposed as a murderer.

499
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:22,060
How could he possibly help us?

500
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:24,730
Even when the rich lose everything,
they're still set for years.

501
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:27,360
He had power and money.
I'm sure he's got a way out.

502
00:30:27,660 --> 00:30:28,870
Let's go, now.

503
00:30:29,170 --> 00:30:30,670
No, I'm not going.

504
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,470
I said let's go!

505
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:34,870
- Now.
- I said no!

506
00:30:47,320 --> 00:30:48,350
Kim Dan Hui.

507
00:30:49,650 --> 00:30:53,720
You must be expecting
to take over as chairman.

508
00:30:58,230 --> 00:31:02,600
But I'll never give up
the chairman's seat.

509
00:31:02,670 --> 00:31:05,100
Hey, Park Tae Ho. You...

510
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:06,870
There you are.

511
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:08,870
Mom, don't!

512
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:15,280
Are you kidding me?

513
00:31:16,210 --> 00:31:17,350
What do you think you're doing?

514
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:20,620
That's what I want to ask you,

515
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,890
you piece of human trash.

516
00:31:22,890 --> 00:31:24,290
Are you even human?

517
00:31:25,050 --> 00:31:28,120
You manipulated
my innocent Yu Na and her father,

518
00:31:29,230 --> 00:31:31,560
and used them to murder CEO Baek.

519
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,760
Choi Yu Na, you...

520
00:31:34,030 --> 00:31:35,370
It wasn't me.

521
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:40,740
So what are you going to do now?
Jin Ju is alive and well,

522
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:44,570
and she's on the warpath
vowing to destroy us all.

523
00:31:45,170 --> 00:31:48,140
Park Tae Ho, you started this mess,
so you'd better fix it.

524
00:31:48,210 --> 00:31:50,110
This is your mess to clean up!

525
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:52,180
My gosh.

526
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:55,080
- Gosh, he's hurting me.
- Mom.

527
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:57,590
Baek Jin Ju?

528
00:31:58,290 --> 00:31:59,290
What?

529
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:02,390
Choi Yu Na, what is she saying?

530
00:32:04,330 --> 00:32:05,330
Well...

531
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,030
My gosh.

532
00:32:08,560 --> 00:32:11,200
Baek Jin Ju is alive. Chloe...

533
00:32:13,070 --> 00:32:14,600
Chloe was Baek Jin Ju all along.

534
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:51,440
(Pearl in Red)

535
00:32:51,670 --> 00:32:53,980
How does someone
who was supposed to be dead...

536
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,480
make it out alive,

537
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:57,080
just to dare to stab me in the back?

538
00:32:57,080 --> 00:32:58,410
Help me from now on.

539
00:32:58,580 --> 00:33:01,380
I need you to stop the chairman
from coming after me.

540
00:33:01,450 --> 00:33:03,490
For now, you'd better figure out
how to save yourself.

541
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:05,460
My only concern at the moment
is my Hyun Jun.

542
00:33:05,620 --> 00:33:07,120
I'm not like Min Jun.

543
00:33:07,360 --> 00:33:08,620
No matter who you killed,

544
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:10,490
the pain I feel is much greater.

545
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:12,930
If Baek Jin Ju tries
to take you down,

546
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:15,600
I will protect you.
That's where I stand.

547
00:33:16,300 --> 00:33:18,300
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
